metadata.name: StarBlock Genesis Pass V2 #1
metadata.description: StarBlock Genesis Pass V2 is an ERC-721 collection on Ethereum, which is the governance NFT of StarBlock NFT Marketplace. Holding it you will have dividend rights, governance rights and special rights in StarBlock. Like Free Mint, SBox, Governance of StarBlock and InsuranceDAO, Tickets to StarBlock Metaspace and StarBlock Genesis Community, Issuing NFT and so on.
